{"tid":104081,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"想買綠置居景泰苑","createTime":"2017-02-01T20:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T07:14:52.000Z","uid":81241,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d88e4e182c8bd7e53725ae76c249acd4c232ed7","tid":104081,"uid":81241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:15:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n本身係綠表<br />\n一個人住緊大埔兩人單位<br />\n想同女朋友買樓結婚<br />\n一直都想買大埔居屋<br />\n大約有百幾萬cash<br />\n壓力測試一定過到<br />\n但大埔居屋400尺綠表都三四百萬<br />\n實在太貴   而且係好舊<br />\n通常都30年樓齡<br />\n我同女友一個翻工翻九龍灣  一個翻工翻天水圍<br />\n見之前景泰苑都算ok個位置咪抽下啦<br />\n但號碼幾後下<br />\n所以無再留意揀唔揀到樓<br />\n<br />\n今日睇到新聞<br />\n發現原來賣唔出  仲有兩成<br />\n個下先發現點解自己唔一早去揀樓<br />\n睇晚原來全部細單位同尾二細單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗左成晚  心大心細<br />\n買唔買293尺尾二細單位<br />\n160-170萬左右<br />\n<br />\n買樓買到好似買菜咁<br />\n係咪唔應該買?!<br />\n一晚決定   真係好趕   好大心理壓力<br />\n大拿拿百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懇求各位巴打大大力屌醒我<br />\n隔多幾個鐘頭我就要同女友去揀樓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9cec4fd3a6c4f531411e9eb76727986dfc1e20","tid":104081,"uid":17645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:25:52.000Z","msg":"300呎都冇買黎把撚咩，租屋住啦"},{"pid":"c4a01bb7207b065f7fae99cab51562655a13dd5c","tid":104081,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:26:46.000Z","msg":"文章入面你已經傾向想買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca712ea88ff006e7b892c6dc2cb3de634b42381","tid":104081,"uid":27961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:28:12.000Z","msg":"呢家d人買樓真係好似買菜咁<br />\n<br />\n我上次去睇新樓都嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces